{"tid":1688290,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟個英文長篇小說上線喇（入面做埋國際文宣）","createTime":"2019-11-02T11:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T11:43:30.000Z","uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"de46d6b9a2efdd1af5ba5dd534bb9d91c6a816e9","tid":1688290,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:05:56.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<br />\n大家想支持既記住like同follow呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/theirs_of_skies/status/1190569720014991361?s=12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftheirs_of_skies%2Fstatus%2F1190569720014991361%3Fs%3D12&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=14eff2c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftheirs_of_skies%2Fstatus%2F1190569720014991361%3Fs%3D12&h=98f07d00\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/theirs_of_skies/status/1190569720014991361?s=12</a>"},{"pid":"a0c1005a0aeccac991991bd9dde722224f121876","tid":1688290,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/su7jeTs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsu7jeTs.png&h=f193bdc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能大家見到英文會擰曬頭<br />\n但呢個故仔一啲都唔離地<br />\n相反佢講緊我哋所有人嘅將來<br />\n呢場運動終有一日會完<br />\n之後既日子亦都得翻我哋自己去面對<br />\n亦都難免會因為我哋嘅取態<br />\n面對反對我哋嘅人既指責<br />\n為我哋所選擇既付出代價<br />\n甚至最後同全中國、全世界反面<br />\n<br />\n「不自由 毋寧死」<br />\n「寧作玉碎 不作瓦全」<br />\n「祈求民主 與自由 萬世都不朽」<br />\n<br />\n「煲底相見」既五年後<br />\n面對已經完成重任既我哋<br />\n仲能唔能夠講番同一番說話？<br />\n如有類同，實屬生蟲<br />\n但真係有咁嘅一日既時候<br />\n我希望我哋仍然可以係「同行兒女 為正義 時代革命」<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港"}]}